OL,6,Fhas confirmed that Professional
OL,7,FStandards are investigating after a
OL,8,Fleaked CCTV video shows a man being
OL,9,Fforcefully restrained by five officers
OL,10,Fwhilst in custody.
OL,12,FThe force has stressed that the public
OL,13,Fshould not reach conclusions without
OL,14,Fbeing aware of the full facts after an
OL,15,Fedited clip went viral online.
OL,17,FThe footage from February has been
OL,18,Fviewed more than 780,000 times on X,
OL,19,Fformerly Twitter.
