OL,4,Cto floor in cell
OL,6,FIt shows a man being restrained,
OL,7,Fstripped and left in a prone position
OL,8,Fby officers in his cell.
OL,10,FHe had been arrested for several
OL,11,Fviolent offences including Grievous
OL,12,FBodily Harm and resisting arrest.
OL,14,FPolice say he continued to be violent
OL,15,Fwhen he was brought into custody,
OL,16,Fmeaning the usual booking procedure
OL,17,Fcould not be completed and he was
OL,18,Ftaken straight to a cell.
