OL,6,FA spokesperson for Guernsey Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "The footage released is an
OL,8,Fedited, standalone clip, which when
OL,9,Fviewed without surrounding context
OL,10,Fdoes, we acknowledge, show officers
OL,11,Fusing force in a way which could cause
OL,12,Fdistress to those who have seen it.
OL,14,F"When detainees are ordinarily brought
OL,15,Finto custody they are asked to change
OL,16,Finto custody-provided clothing if
OL,17,Fthere are concerns around the state of
OL,18,Fthe detainee, their safety or the
OL,19,Fsafety of others.
