OL,6,F"Officers would ask detainees to do
OL,7,Fthis voluntarily, but if this does not
OL,8,Fhappen officers must ensure it
OL,9,Fhappens, as per our procedures.
OL,11,F"Guernsey Police would strongly urge
OL,12,Fmembers of the community against
OL,13,Fjudging the actions of officers
OL,14,Fthrough edited versions of CCTV and
OL,15,Freach conclusions via the 'court of
OL,16,Fpublic opinion' and social media,
OL,17,Fwithout being aware of the full facts.
