OL,6,F"The matter has been brought to the
OL,7,Fattention of our Professional
OL,8,FStandards Department and we want to
OL,9,Fassure the community we will take all
OL,10,Fappropriate steps if there is any
OL,11,Finference of misconduct."
OL,13,FPolice add that the man being
OL,14,Frestrained in the footage has pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to the offences for which he
OL,16,Fwas charged and is currently in prison.
OL,18,FITV News has seen a ten-page complaint
OL,19,Fletter from him, alleging a list of
OL,20,Ffailings in how the case was handled.
